translations:
lemma not_ks [simp]:                                      
   "(x \<noteq> kno) = (x = unk)"
   "(x \<noteq> unk) = (x = kno)"

proof (prove)
goal (1 subgoal):
 1. (x \<noteq> kno) = (x = unk) &&& (x \<noteq> unk) = (x = kno)

lemma not_ps [simp]:
  "(x \<noteq> noreq) = (x = req)"
  "(x \<noteq> req) = (x = noreq)"

proof (prove)
goal (1 subgoal):
 1. (x \<noteq> noreq) = (x = req) &&& (x \<noteq> req) = (x = noreq)

lemma not_ffs [simp]:
  "(x \<noteq> val) = (x = inv)"
  "(x \<noteq> inv) = (x = val)"

proof (prove)
goal (1 subgoal):
 1. (x \<noteq> val) = (x = Aodv_Basic.inv) &&&
    (x \<noteq> Aodv_Basic.inv) = (x = val)
